    <item>
      <title>全球市场危机加剧，大宗商品面临危机蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/commodities-face-contagion-as-global-market-meltdown-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球经济低迷导致工业需求前景黯淡，且交易商纷纷套现获利，从铜、黄金到原油等大宗商品价格均大幅下跌，但跌幅有所收窄。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/commodities-face-contagion-as-global-market-meltdown-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:25:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
